title: Crafted for non-standard UI design projects
text: Designed primarily for unconventional, brutal, or minimalist websites.

title: Made in Figma, useful everywhere
text: Completely compatible with the newest 2022 component properties and override features of Figma.

title: 2px stroke weight default
text: For aesthetically balanced icons across sizes, the default stroke weight is 2px. As an alternative we offer a thing 1px stroke weight version.

title: 1,920+ and counting
text: Packed of everything you need to create unconventional user interfaces and websites.

title: 4+ flexible styles
text: Choose between line, solid or thin icon styles. In the future, there will be more style available for free!

title: Use in countless projects
text: This is how we intended it to workâ€”to be the most impartial, adaptable, and scalable library that could be used for any project.

title: Optimized SVG output
text: There are no extra layers or forms. SVG outputs are designed to be infinitely scaleable, have a small file size, and have no extraneous properties.

title: Lifetime updates
text: No paid upgrades or subscriptions. Pay once, receive updates for life. In addition you can request new icons via mail or GitHub!
